Ayub onyiso pok ma joricho yudo


1  Ayub ne omedo wacho niya,


2  “Akuong’ora e nyim Nyasaye Mangima Manyalo Gik moko Duto,

motamore ng’adona bura makare,

kendo mosemiyo chunya obedo malit,


3  ni, e kinde duto moweya ka angima,


4  to dhoga ok nowach gimoro marach,

kendo lewa ok nomul miriambo.


5  E ndalo duto ma pod angima,

ok nayie ni wecheu ni kare,

to nasik kawacho ni aonge gi ketho.


6  Ok nawe mak awacho ni an kare,

nimar ang’eyo ni aler.


7  Mad jogo duto ma piem koda yud kum mana ka joricho.


8  Ere geno ma joma ok gen Nyasaye di bedgo,

e sa ma Nyasaye dwaro negogie.


9  Koso Nyasaye diwinj ywakgi ka chandruok omakogi?


10  Ne onego ginyis ni giyudo mor kuom tiyo ni Nyasaye,

bende nonego gibed ka gilame pile!


11  Koro we mondo apuonjue kaka duong’ mar Nyasayee romo,

kendo mondo anyisue gima Ng’ama Nyalo Gik Moko Duto osechano.


12  To bende kata ka ok anyisou, to useneno gi wang’u,

koro ere gima omiyo uwacho weche manono?


13  Winjuru kaka Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto kumo joricho

kod joma timo timbe mahundu.


14  Nyalo bet ni gin gi yawuowi mang’eny,

to giduto ginitho e lweny,

kendo nyithindgi bende ok noyud chiemo moromogi.


15  Eka tuo to noneg joma otony e lweny kata ma kech ok onego,

kendo mondgi ok noywaggi.


16  Jaricho nyalo bet gi pesa mang’eny ka lowo,

kendo nyalo bet gi lewni mogundho ma okia kar kwan-gi,


17  to lepego ng’at moro makare ema biro rwako,

kendo ng’at moro ma onge ketho ema biro kawo pesanego.


18  Joricho gero udi, to utgigo ok nyal dak.

Girumo piyo mana ka mbuwi kata ka kiru.


19  Chieng’ moro nindo notergi ka pod gimew,

to ka gichiew, to giniyud ka mwandugi oselal.


20  Masira nomakgi ka ohula motucho apoya,

kendo yamb otieno nokegi mabor.


21  Adier, yamb ugue noywergi ka gologi e miechgi.


22  Enokudh kuomgi matek, ma ok oweyonigi thuolo,

kendo kata obedo ni ginitem kaka ginyalo mondo gitony,


23  to yamo nokudh kuomgi ka giringo,

kendo tekone malich nomi kihondko makgi.

